OL,3,CGeldof's threat to quit Blair's Africa
OL,4,CCommission
OL,6,FA furious Bob Geldof threatened to
OL,7,Fstorm out of Tony Blair's Commission
OL,8,Ffor Africa ` warning it was in danger
OL,9,Fof becoming "a laughable grotesque",
OL,10,Faccording to newly-released government
OL,11,Ffiles.
OL,13,FThe Live Aid campaigner was
OL,14,Finstrumental in persuading Mr Blair to
OL,15,Fset up the commission to examine the
OL,16,Fproblems of the continent ahead of a
OL,17,Fcrucial summit of the G8 at Gleneagles
OL,18,Fin Scotland, which the UK was chairing.
