OL,6,FBut official papers released to the
OL,7,FNational Archives in Kew, west London,
OL,8,Fshow he was outraged when ` after just
OL,9,Fone meeting ` the commissioners were
OL,10,Fsent a document setting its "emerging
OL,11,Fconclusions".
OL,13,FIn an angry letter to the commission's
OL,14,Fdirector of policy, the economist Sir
OL,15,FNick Stern, dated August 9 2004, he
OL,16,Fsaid it was impossible to have come to
OL,17,Fany conclusions it such a short period
OL,18,Fof time.
