OL,6,FThe former rock star warned that he
OL,7,Fwas not prepared to serve on a body
OL,8,Fwhich was simply there to push "pre-
OL,9,Fdetermined government policy".
OL,11,F"To be clear, policy must be
OL,12,Fdetermined by the commission
OL,13,Findependently sitting and
OL,14,Findependently deliberating and
OL,15,Fconcluding of its own volition. This
OL,16,Fdistinction is vital. If I have got
OL,17,Fthis wrong please inform me so I may
OL,18,Ftender my resignation," he wrote.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@]O]sD@AOUzD@WO]
