OL,6,F"More broadly, the whole notion of
OL,7,Femerging solutions is laughable. If
OL,8,Fthe solution to the misery of Africa
OL,9,Fcan be 'concluded' within a mere six
OL,10,Fweek time span, it is a truly
OL,11,Fremarkable feat.
OL,13,F"How blind we must all have been these
OL,14,Fpast years. The fact is that there are
OL,15,Fnot and cannot as yet be any emerging
OL,16,Fconclusions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
