OL,6,F"The commission will lose all
OL,7,Fcredibility if it is not clearly seen
OL,8,Fto be an independent entity. If it
OL,9,Fseems to advance pre-determined
OL,10,Fgovernment policy it will be correctly
OL,11,Fviewed as a laughable grotesque."
OL,13,FGeldof went on to complain that the
OL,14,Finvolvement of some of the
OL,15,Fcommissioners ` including some of
OL,16,Fthose from Africa ` appeared to have
OL,17,Fbeen "minimal".
