OL,4,CCommission
OL,6,F"Is it not the secretariat's function,
OL,7,Fon behalf of the chair, to ensure that
OL,8,Fthis is not the case? Or is this all
OL,9,Fsome farcical political game played
OL,10,Fout at the expense of the wretchedly
OL,11,Fpoor? If so, I ain't playing."
OL,13,FSir Nicholas wrote back hurriedly to
OL,14,Fassure him the that the document was
OL,15,Fnot an attempt pre-empt the
OL,16,Fcommission's findings, and that the
OL,17,Finput from British politicians had
OL,18,Fbeen "comparatively minor".
