OL,6,F"Far from being an attempt to rush
OL,7,Fconclusions the paper is intended to
OL,8,Fto be a tool to help promote
OL,9,Fdiscussion and ensure a real
OL,10,Finterchange between commissioners at
OL,11,Fthe second meeting in October," he
OL,12,Fwrote.
OL,14,F"I would be very keen to sit down and
OL,15,Fdiscuss these questions with you;
OL,16,Fperhaps we could meet for a drink as
OL,17,Fsoon as we are both around?"
OL,19,FGeldof's reply is not recorded in the
OL,20,Ffiles, but he was sufficiently
OL,21,Fplacated to carry on.
